VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# Production site origin for Supabase auth emails (password reset). If unset, the app uses the current browser origin
# (localhost in dev — reset links in email will point at localhost). Set on Vercel to your live URL, e.g.:
# VITE_SITE_URL=https://your-app.vercel.app

# Optional: cross-domain legal links (defaults are /privacy, /terms, /sms-consent on same host).
# Example when SMS consent is only on Vercel and privacy/terms on www.tradesman-us.com:
# VITE_PUBLIC_PRIVACY_URL=https://www.tradesman-us.com/privacy
# VITE_PUBLIC_TERMS_URL=https://www.tradesman-us.com/terms
# VITE_PUBLIC_SMS_CONSENT_URL=https://tradesman.vercel.app/sms-consent

# Optional: sidebar + Account “Help Desk” display (defaults: (844) 844-1611 / +18448441611)
# VITE_HELP_DESK_PHONE_DISPLAY=(844) 844-1611
# VITE_HELP_DESK_PHONE_E164=+18448441611

# --- Vercel / serverless (set in Vercel → Project → Environment Variables) ---
# Copy from Supabase Project Settings → API (same project as VITE_*).
# Serverless /api/* routes do NOT read the Vite bundle; set these explicitly for Production (and Preview if you use it):
# SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<same value as VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY>
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=<service_role secret — never expose to the browser>
#
# Required for: Twilio webhooks (help desk, voicemail greeting save, trouble tickets), help desk greeting save, storage uploads.
# Admin trouble-ticket recording playback (/api/twilio-recording): SUPABASE_URL + SUPABASE_ANON_KEY (or VITE_*), or SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY if anon is not on serverless.
#
# Help desk: record MAIN opening greeting by phone (menu action "Main help desk greeting"):
# HELP_DESK_GREETING_RECORD_PIN=123456   (digits only, 4–12 chars; you enter this on the phone before recording)
# RESEND_API_KEY=re_...
# RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=Tradesman <onboarding@your-verified-domain.com>
# TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=...
# TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=...
# Optional SMS fallback if no DB channel: TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER=+1...
# Optional custom SMS bridge: SMS_OUTBOUND_WEBHOOK_URL=https://...

# --- Supabase Edge Functions (same names; set in Dashboard or CLI, not in this file) ---
# Dashboard: Project Settings → Edge Functions → Manage secrets
# CLI: supabase secrets set TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=AC... TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=...
# Use LIVE credentials for production (same as Vercel). See supabase/TWILIO_SECRETS.txt

# Supabase Auth (Dashboard → Authentication):
# - Site URL: your production app origin (e.g. https://your-app.vercel.app).
# - Redirect URLs: include https://your-app.vercel.app/reset-password (and http://localhost:5173/reset-password for Vite dev if needed).
# - Optional: paste branded HTML from supabase/email-templates/password-recovery.html into the Reset password template.
# For production email confirmation, configure SMTP or a provider (e.g. Resend) in Supabase → Project Settings → Auth.
